message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think it would be perfect for you. I'm asking for $16,000 to start the conversation.  What do you think?

Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of the product is high to you, but I am only willing to pay up to $12,000 for it. I hope we can come to an agreement that works for both of us.
